+frameInbox('Raison d\'etre')
    div
        ul
            li.fragment(data-fragment-index='1') game development is a world with many heroes, a few stars and a very few superstars
            li.fragment(data-fragment-index='2') developers make games for the same reason why writers write books or painters paint paintings
            li.highlight-2.fragment(data-fragment-index='3') it is a way to leave creative footprints and express ideas to the world  
        .text-center.mt-20.fragment(data-fragment-index='1')
            img.height-600(src=imgAssets+'kingdom_come.jpg')